        "content": "<p>I've noticed that:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elm\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"err\">##</span><span class=\"kt\">This</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">valid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">doc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">comment</span>\n<span class=\"kt\">User</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">name</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"kt\">Str</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"err\">##</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">This</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">valid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">doc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">comment</span>\n<span class=\"kt\">User</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">name</span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"kt\">Str</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is it intentional for comments with ## but without a starting space to not be treated as doc comments?</p>",
